headline.main: No Evidence of Trump's Obama Wiretap Claim, Republican Lawmaker Says
headline.print_headline: No Evidence of Trump's Obama Wiretap Claim, Republican Lawmaker Says

lead_paragraph: A Republican lawmaker who heads a House of Representatives oversight panel said on Monday he had seen no direct evidence to back U.S. President Donald Trump's assertion that his predecessor, Barack Obama, wiretapped him.
